{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1520,"text":"In case you are wondering,"},{"time":3280,"text":"no, I'm not wearing a dress,"},{"time":6840,"text":"and no, I'm not saying\nwhat I'm wearing underneath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13320,"text":"This is a gho."},{"time":15920,"text":"This is my national dress."},{"time":18200,"text":"This is how all men dress in Bhutan."},{"time":22520,"text":"That is how our women dress."},{"time":26320,"text":"Like our women,"},{"time":28520,"text":"we men get to wear pretty bright colors,"},{"time":32960,"text":"but unlike our women,"},{"time":35240,"text":"we get to show off our legs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38880,"text":"Our national dress is unique,"},{"time":40320,"text":"but this is not the only thing\nthat's unique about my country."},{"time":44040,"text":"Our promise to remain\ncarbon neutral is also unique,"},{"time":47200,"text":"and this is what I'd like\nto speak about today,"},{"time":49440,"text":"our promise to remain carbon neutral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52720,"text":"But before I proceed,\nI should set you the context."},{"time":56680,"text":"I should tell you our story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59440,"text":"Bhutan is a small country\nin the Himalayas."},{"time":64160,"text":"We've been called Shangri-La,"},{"time":66320,"text":"even the last Shangri-La."},{"time":69040,"text":"But let me tell you right off the bat,\nwe are not Shangri-La."},{"time":72480,"text":"My country is not one big monastery"},{"time":75240,"text":"populated with happy monks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78600,"text":"The reality is that\nthere are barely 700,000 of us"},{"time":84320,"text":"sandwiched between two\nof the most populated countries on earth,"},{"time":89280,"text":"China and India."},{"time":92760,"text":"The reality is that we are a small,\nunderdeveloped country"},{"time":96560,"text":"doing our best to survive."},{"time":99600,"text":"But we are doing OK. We are surviving."},{"time":103000,"text":"In fact, we are thriving,"},{"time":106320,"text":"and the reason we are thriving\nis because we've been blessed"},{"time":110800,"text":"with extraordinary kings."},{"time":113120,"text":"Our enlightened monarchs\nhave worked tirelessly"},{"time":116160,"text":"to develop our country,"},{"time":118040,"text":"balancing economic growth carefully"},{"time":121640,"text":"with social development,\nenvironmental sustainability"},{"time":124560,"text":"and cultural preservation,"},{"time":126440,"text":"all within the framework\nof good governance."},{"time":130199,"text":"We call this holistic approach\nto development"},{"time":133080,"text":"\"Gross National Happiness,\" or GNH."},{"time":137440,"text":"Back in the 1970s,"},{"time":139480,"text":"our fourth king famously\npronounced that for Bhutan,"},{"time":143040,"text":"Gross National Happiness is more important\nthan Gross National Product."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147600,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152400,"text":"Ever since,"},{"time":154320,"text":"all development in Bhutan\nis driven by GNH,"},{"time":159080,"text":"a pioneering vision\nthat aims to improve the happiness"},{"time":163000,"text":"and well-being of our people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166760,"text":"But that's easier said than done,"},{"time":168960,"text":"especially when you are one\nof the smallest economies in the world."},{"time":173360,"text":"Our entire GDP is less\nthan two billion dollars."},{"time":177920,"text":"I know that some of you here\nare worth more --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181720,"text":"individually"},{"time":183280,"text":"than the entire economy of my country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188640,"text":"So our economy is small,"},{"time":190880,"text":"but here is where it gets interesting."},{"time":194000,"text":"Education is completely free."},{"time":196360,"text":"All citizens are guaranteed\nfree school education,"},{"time":199440,"text":"and those that work hard\nare given free college education."},{"time":202440,"text":"Healthcare is also completely free."},{"time":204920,"text":"Medical consultation,\nmedical treatment, medicines:"},{"time":208000,"text":"they are all provided by the state."},{"time":211440,"text":"We manage this"},{"time":213560,"text":"because we use our limited\nresources very carefully,"},{"time":217600,"text":"and because we stay faithful\nto the core mission of GNH,"},{"time":223280,"text":"which is development with values."},{"time":227600,"text":"Our economy is small,\nand we must strengthen it."},{"time":230520,"text":"Economic growth is important,"},{"time":232720,"text":"but that economic growth must not come\nfrom undermining our unique culture"},{"time":237880,"text":"or our pristine environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242680,"text":"Today, our culture is flourishing."},{"time":245080,"text":"We continue to celebrate\nour art and architecture,"},{"time":248800,"text":"food and festivals,"},{"time":251880,"text":"monks and monasteries."},{"time":254760,"text":"And yes, we celebrate\nour national dress, too."},{"time":260480,"text":"This is why I can wear my gho with pride."},{"time":265200,"text":"Here's a fun fact:"},{"time":267520,"text":"you're looking\nat the world's biggest pocket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273120,"text":"It starts here,"},{"time":275160,"text":"goes around the back,"},{"time":277360,"text":"and comes out from inside here."},{"time":280400,"text":"In this pocket"},{"time":281920,"text":"we store all manner of personal goods"},{"time":284960,"text":"from phones and wallets"},{"time":288280,"text":"to iPads, office files and books."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":292560,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":294280,"text":"But sometimes --"},{"time":296840,"text":"sometimes even precious cargo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302200,"text":"So our culture is flourishing,"},{"time":304560,"text":"but so is our environment."},{"time":307040,"text":"72 percent of my country\nis under forest cover."},{"time":311440,"text":"Our constitution demands\nthat a minimum of 60 percent"},{"time":316440,"text":"of Bhutan's total land\nshall remain under forest cover"},{"time":320160,"text":"for all time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":327080,"text":"Our constitution,"},{"time":329240,"text":"this constitution,"},{"time":332000,"text":"imposes forest cover on us."},{"time":335880,"text":"Incidentally, our king\nused this constitution"},{"time":340120,"text":"to impose democracy on us."},{"time":342640,"text":"You see, we the people\ndidn't want democracy."},{"time":345840,"text":"We didn't ask for it, we didn't demand it,"},{"time":348840,"text":"and we certainly didn't fight for it."},{"time":351280,"text":"Instead, our king imposed democracy on us"},{"time":356000,"text":"by insisting that he include it\nin the constitution."},{"time":360520,"text":"But he went further."},{"time":362480,"text":"He included provisions in the constitution"},{"time":366320,"text":"that empower the people\nto impeach their kings,"},{"time":370080,"text":"and included provisions in here\nthat require all our kings to retire"},{"time":375640,"text":"at the age of 65."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379920,"text":"Fact is, we already have\na king in retirement:"},{"time":384840,"text":"our previous king, the Great Fourth,"},{"time":388160,"text":"retired 10 years ago"},{"time":390640,"text":"at the peak of his popularity."},{"time":393720,"text":"He was all of 51 years at that time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399080,"text":"So as I was saying,"},{"time":401480,"text":"72 percent of our country\nis under forest cover,"},{"time":404920,"text":"and all that forest is pristine."},{"time":407720,"text":"That's why we are one of the few remaining"},{"time":410120,"text":"global biodiversity hotspots in the world,"},{"time":413160,"text":"and that's why we are\na carbon neutral country."},{"time":416360,"text":"In a world that is threatened\nwith climate change,"},{"time":418720,"text":"we are a carbon neutral country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423480,"text":"Turns out, it's a big deal."},{"time":425920,"text":"Of the 200-odd countries\nin the world today,"},{"time":428320,"text":"it looks like we are the only one"},{"time":430560,"text":"that's carbon neutral."},{"time":433520,"text":"Actually, that's not quite accurate."},{"time":437040,"text":"Bhutan is not carbon neutral."},{"time":439920,"text":"Bhutan is carbon negative."},{"time":443600,"text":"Our entire country generates\n2.2 million tons of carbon dioxide,"},{"time":450560,"text":"but our forests, they sequester\nmore than three times that amount,"},{"time":455720,"text":"so we are a net carbon sink"},{"time":457880,"text":"for more than four million tons\nof carbon dioxide each year."},{"time":463160,"text":"But that's not all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":466560,"text":"We export most\nof the renewable electricity"},{"time":469680,"text":"we generate from our fast-flowing rivers."},{"time":473160,"text":"So today, the clean energy that we export"},{"time":476600,"text":"offsets about six million tons\nof carbon dioxide in our neighborhood."},{"time":482240,"text":"By 2020, we'll be exporting\nenough electricity"},{"time":486200,"text":"to offset 17 million tons\nof carbon dioxide."},{"time":490680,"text":"And if we were to harness\neven half our hydropower potential,"},{"time":493960,"text":"and that's exactly what we are working at,"},{"time":497120,"text":"the clean, green energy that we export"},{"time":499520,"text":"would offset something like\n50 million tons of carbon dioxide a year."},{"time":506320,"text":"That is more CO2 than what the entire city\nof New York generates in one year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513159,"text":"So inside our country,\nwe are a net carbon sink."},{"time":516280,"text":"Outside, we are offsetting carbon."},{"time":518840,"text":"And this is important stuff."},{"time":521240,"text":"You see, the world is getting warmer,"},{"time":523840,"text":"and climate change is a reality."},{"time":527440,"text":"Climate change is affecting my country."},{"time":530280,"text":"Our glaciers are melting,"},{"time":532360,"text":"causing flash floods and landslides,"},{"time":534880,"text":"which in turn are causing disaster\nand widespread destruction in our country."},{"time":541560,"text":"I was at that lake recently."},{"time":543760,"text":"It's stunning."},{"time":546240,"text":"That's how it looked 10 years ago,"},{"time":549240,"text":"and that's how it looked 20 years ago."},{"time":552320,"text":"Just 20 years ago, that lake didn't exist."},{"time":555880,"text":"It was a solid glacier."},{"time":559520,"text":"A few years ago, a similar lake"},{"time":562760,"text":"breached its dams"},{"time":565920,"text":"and wreaked havoc in the valleys below."},{"time":570360,"text":"That destruction\nwas caused by one glacier lake."},{"time":573400,"text":"We have 2,700 of them to contend with."},{"time":578640,"text":"The point is this:"},{"time":580800,"text":"my country and my people have done nothing"},{"time":584640,"text":"to contribute to global warming,"},{"time":587920,"text":"but we are already bearing the brunt\nof its consequences."},{"time":593640,"text":"And for a small, poor country,\none that is landlocked and mountainous,"},{"time":597600,"text":"it is very difficult."},{"time":600320,"text":"But we are not going to sit\non our hands doing nothing."},{"time":602960,"text":"We will fight climate change."},{"time":604920,"text":"That's why we have promised\nto remain carbon neutral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610480,"text":"We first made this promise in 2009"},{"time":614840,"text":"during COP 15 in Copenhagen,"},{"time":618800,"text":"but nobody noticed."},{"time":620960,"text":"Governments were so busy\narguing with one another"},{"time":623640,"text":"and blaming each other\nfor causing climate change,"},{"time":626600,"text":"that when a small country\nraised our hands and announced,"},{"time":630280,"text":"\"We promise to remain\ncarbon neutral for all time,\""},{"time":633400,"text":"nobody heard us."},{"time":635880,"text":"Nobody cared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639400,"text":"Last December in Paris,"},{"time":642480,"text":"at COP 21, we reiterated our promise"},{"time":645760,"text":"to remain carbon neutral\nfor all time to come."},{"time":649760,"text":"This time, we were heard."},{"time":651880,"text":"We were noticed, and everybody cared."},{"time":657200,"text":"What was different in Paris\nwas that governments came round together"},{"time":662160,"text":"to accept the realities of climate change,"},{"time":664800,"text":"and were willing to come together\nand act together and work together."},{"time":669000,"text":"All countries, from the very small\nto the very large,"},{"time":673440,"text":"committed to reduce\nthe greenhouse gas emissions."},{"time":678680,"text":"The UN Framework Convention\non Climate Change"},{"time":681800,"text":"says that if these so-called\nintended commitments are kept,"},{"time":687400,"text":"we'd be closer\nto containing global warming"},{"time":689640,"text":"by two degrees Celsius."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694440,"text":"By the way,"},{"time":696640,"text":"I've requested the TED organizers here"},{"time":699400,"text":"to turn up the heat in here\nby two degrees,"},{"time":704520,"text":"so if some of you\nare feeling warmer than usual,"},{"time":707360,"text":"you know who to blame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711520,"text":"It's crucial that all of us\nkeep our commitments."},{"time":715600,"text":"As far as Bhutan is concerned,"},{"time":717080,"text":"we will keep our promise\nto remain carbon neutral."},{"time":721560,"text":"Here are some of the ways we are doing it."},{"time":724760,"text":"We are providing free electricity\nto our rural farmers."},{"time":728240,"text":"The idea is that, with free electricity,\nthey will no longer have to use firewood"},{"time":734560,"text":"to cook their food."},{"time":736520,"text":"We are investing in sustainable transport"},{"time":739360,"text":"and subsidizing the purchase\nof electric vehicles."},{"time":742840,"text":"Similarly, we are subsidizing\nthe cost of LED lights,"},{"time":747000,"text":"and our entire government\nis trying to go paperless."},{"time":751320,"text":"We are cleaning up our entire country\nthrough Clean Bhutan, a national program,"},{"time":755840,"text":"and we are planting trees\nthroughout our country"},{"time":759000,"text":"through Green Bhutan,"},{"time":761160,"text":"another national program."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764320,"text":"But it is our protected areas"},{"time":766520,"text":"that are at the core\nof our carbon neutral strategy."},{"time":770320,"text":"Our protected areas are our carbon sink."},{"time":773560,"text":"They are our lungs."},{"time":776880,"text":"Today, more than half\nour country is protected,"},{"time":780400,"text":"as national parks, nature reserves"},{"time":782800,"text":"and wildlife sanctuaries."},{"time":785400,"text":"But the beauty is that we've connected\nthem all with one another"},{"time":789520,"text":"through a network of biological corridors."},{"time":794120,"text":"Now, what this means"},{"time":795400,"text":"is that our animals are free\nto roam throughout our country."},{"time":801760,"text":"Take this tiger, for example."},{"time":803200,"text":"It was spotted\nat 250 meters above sea level"},{"time":806920,"text":"in the hot, subtropical jungles."},{"time":810040,"text":"Two years later, that same tiger"},{"time":813040,"text":"was spotted near 4,000 meters"},{"time":816560,"text":"in our cold alpine mountains."},{"time":819840,"text":"Isn't that awesome?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":821720,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825800,"text":"We must keep it that way."},{"time":828480,"text":"We must keep our parks awesome."},{"time":831840,"text":"So every year, we set aside resources\nto prevent poaching, hunting,"},{"time":836560,"text":"mining and pollution in our parks,"},{"time":838960,"text":"and resources to help communities\nwho live in those parks"},{"time":844120,"text":"manage their forests,"},{"time":845640,"text":"adapt to climate change,"},{"time":847120,"text":"and lead better lives while continuing\nto live in harmony with Mother Nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852600,"text":"But that is expensive."},{"time":854640,"text":"Over the next few years,\nour small economy won't have the resources"},{"time":860400,"text":"to cover all the costs that are required\nto protect our environment."},{"time":865560,"text":"In fact, when we run the numbers,"},{"time":867200,"text":"it looks like it'll take us\nat least 15 years"},{"time":869920,"text":"before we can fully finance\nall our conservation efforts."},{"time":875280,"text":"But neither Bhutan,"},{"time":877720,"text":"nor the world"},{"time":879480,"text":"can afford to spend 15 years\ngoing backwards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884600,"text":"This is why His Majesty the King"},{"time":887720,"text":"started Bhutan For Life."},{"time":890320,"text":"Bhutan For Life gives us the time we need."},{"time":892920,"text":"It gives us breathing room."},{"time":895120,"text":"It is essentially a funding mechanism"},{"time":897520,"text":"to look after our parks,"},{"time":899480,"text":"to protect our parks,"},{"time":901680,"text":"until our government\ncan take over on our own fully."},{"time":905720,"text":"The idea is to raise a transition fund"},{"time":909520,"text":"from individual donors,\ncorporations and institutions,"},{"time":913840,"text":"but the deal is closed only\nafter predetermined conditions are met"},{"time":918400,"text":"and all funds committed."},{"time":920920,"text":"So multiparty, single closing:"},{"time":924360,"text":"an idea we borrowed from Wall Street."},{"time":927680,"text":"This means that individual donors\ncan commit without having to worry"},{"time":932000,"text":"that they'll be left\nsupporting an underfunded plan."},{"time":937480,"text":"It's something like a Kickstarter project,"},{"time":939760,"text":"only with a 15-year time horizon"},{"time":942160,"text":"and millions of tons\nof carbon dioxide at stake."},{"time":946400,"text":"Once the deal is closed,"},{"time":949320,"text":"we use the transition fund\nto protect our parks,"},{"time":953400,"text":"giving our government time\nto increase our own funding gradually"},{"time":958600,"text":"until the end of the 15-year period."},{"time":960640,"text":"After that, our government\nguarantees full funding forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968120,"text":"We are almost there."},{"time":969800,"text":"We expect to close later this year."},{"time":972640,"text":"Naturally, I'm pretty excited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974360,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":980280,"text":"The World Wildlife Fund\nis our principle partner in this journey,"},{"time":986960,"text":"and I want to give them a big shoutout"},{"time":989040,"text":"for the excellent work\nthey are doing in Bhutan"},{"time":992160,"text":"and across the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":993440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":997040,"text":"Whew, it is getting warm in here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012320,"text":"I thank you for listening to our story,"},{"time":1015120,"text":"a story of how we are keeping\nour promise to remain carbon neutral,"},{"time":1019680,"text":"a story of how we are keeping\nour country pristine,"},{"time":1024359,"text":"for ourselves, our children,"},{"time":1026760,"text":"for your children and for the world."},{"time":1030560,"text":"But we are not here\nto tell stories, are we?"},{"time":1033640,"text":"We are here to dream together."},{"time":1037319,"text":"So in closing, I'd like to share\none more dream that I have."},{"time":1042200,"text":"What if we could mobilize\nour leadership and our resources,"},{"time":1045839,"text":"our influence and our passion,"},{"time":1048520,"text":"to replicate the Bhutan For Life idea\nto other countries"},{"time":1051840,"text":"so that they too"},{"time":1054640,"text":"can conserve their\nprotected areas for all time."},{"time":1058160,"text":"After all, there are many other countries\nwho face the same issues that we face."},{"time":1061946,"text":"They too have natural resources"},{"time":1064160,"text":"that can help win the world's fight\nfor sustainability,"},{"time":1068160,"text":"only they may not have the ability\nto invest in them now."},{"time":1071080,"text":"So what if we set up Earth For Life,"},{"time":1074120,"text":"a global fund, to kickstart\nthe Bhutan For Life throughout the world?"},{"time":1080320,"text":"I invite you to help me,"},{"time":1082720,"text":"to carry this dream beyond our borders"},{"time":1085200,"text":"to all those who care\nabout our planet's future."},{"time":1090880,"text":"After all, we're here to dream together,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"to work together,"},{"time":1096800,"text":"to fight climate change together,\nto protect our planet together."},{"time":1101080,"text":"Because the reality is"},{"time":1104280,"text":"we are in it together."},{"time":1106720,"text":"Some of us might dress differently,"},{"time":1109520,"text":"but we are in it together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111720,"text":"Thank you very much,"},{"time":1113320,"text":"and kadrin chhe la. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1115240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1116880,"text":"Thank you, thank you, thank you."}]}]}